text: Emil Sylvegård (born 2 March 1993) is a Swedish professional ice hockey forward for Malmö Redhawks of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Sylvegård made his SHL debut playing with Luleå HF during the 2014–15 SHL season. == References == == External links == * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Asplöven HC players Category:Drummondville Voltigeurs players Category:Expatriate ice hockey players in Canada Category:Linköping HC players Category:Luleå HF players Category:Malmö Redhawks players Category:IK Oskarshamn players Category:Regina Pats players Category:Swedish expatriate sportspeople in Canada Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
